room_title: Escape room "1776" by The Escape Room Fishers in Indianapolis
review: We had 5 people and our Master Miriam. First time doing an escape room. Our family has had a lot of laughs from our adventure. We escaped with 1:58 to go. We cant wait to go back!

room_title: Escape room "1776" by The Escape Room Fishers in Indianapolis
review: 1776 is the first room my wife and I beat with my in-laws. We did not know if they would enjoy these games, but we were pleasantly surprised when they absolutely loved it!  The theme and difficultly was perfect for their first time. We talked about escape room games for hours at the brewery across the street after we were done.

room_title: Escape room "1776" by The Escape Room Fishers in Indianapolis
review: Our family did the 1776 room last night and had a blast! Our game host was named Amelia and she was so nice and did a great job! We can't wait to come back and do more rooms!!!

room_title: Escape room "1776" by The Escape Room Fishers in Indianapolis
review: We did the 1776 room and had a blast. Delani, our Sergeant for the day was so much fun! What a great experience!

room_title: Escape room "1776" by The Escape Room Fishers in Indianapolis
review: Enjoyed the whole experience. Nice lounge area and drink selection and the 1776 Room was really well done. Delani did a great job.

room_title: Escape room "1776" by The Escape Room Fishers in Indianapolis
review: First time doing an escape room. 1776 was awesome and Amelia did a great job telling us what to do. Lots of fun for a group outing.

room_title: Escape room "1776" by The Escape Room Fishers in Indianapolis
review: We had a phenomenal experience in the 1776 room with the family. Delina (not sure if spelling correctly) was an awesome host and made our time here remarkable.
